text: Famous people are famous because of gifts they have been given. Legends become important for the gifts they give. Senator McCain is a legend.
How in such a short period of time has our country moved from the civility of Senator McCain to what we have today? How can we explain this spiral lower to our children and grandchildren?
Nobody wants to hear from you today. Nobody.
